## Alarm System Workflow
```mermaid
graph TD
    I((Android System AlarmManager Detects Trigger Time)) --> J{PendingIntent Executed}
    J --> K[Intent Broadcast to AlarmReceiver]
    subgraph Your Application
        K --> L{AlarmReceiver onReceive()}
        L --> M[Extracts alarmId title from Intent]
        M --> N[Creates Intent for AlarmService with alarmId title]
        N --> O{AlarmService onStartCommand or Foreground Service}
        O --> P[Performs Alarm Action e.g. Notification Sound]
    end
    style I fill:#f8cecc,stroke:#b85450,stroke-width:2px
